{"tid":1695570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大反送中傳說","createTime":"2019-11-05T17:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T17:05:10.000Z","uid":160998,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b10e8ab23ec8f723693031a5713bfe4fde37a1a","tid":1695570,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"1.黨鐵職員前線好黃 唔好再拆黨鐵 唔好為難前線<br />\n會逆轉民意！！<br />\n<br />\n2.警察有白警 唔好再屌狗 <br />\n會逆轉民意！！<br />\n<br />\n3.TVB前線記者係黃 唔好再阻住佢地採訪！！<br />\n會逆轉民意！！<br />\n<br />\n4.藍絲雖然斬人但係佢地都係 唔好再召喚神獸！！<br />\n會逆轉民意！！<br />\n<br />\n5.共產黨會答應五大訴求 並考慮清算黑警 已階段性勝利 唔好再抗爭啦！！<br />\n會逆轉民意！！<br />\n<br />\n見好就收啦！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦你地班五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />逆轉你老母啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16031f87210c956fc91ce34a70f760bce170200","tid":1695570,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:00:40.000Z","msg":"img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/a2YVYz6.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2YVYz6.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=63438be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/a2YVYz6.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n簡單嚟講 輪更制係膽，玩法就百搭。<br />\n輪更就係要班狗出嚟<br />\n佢一出嚟商場/街鋪就會落閘<br />\n借班狗嚟攬炒經濟<br />\n<br />\n而大家所付出既只係一日假期<br />\n<br />\n唔洗衝唔洗守唔洗打<br />\n如果冇狗<br />\n就做自己野，人多就會冇位企<br />\n黨鐵就會早收關站<br />\n<br />\n咁班狗出唔出嚟好？🤤<br />\n<br />\n有狗就街坊裝入商場/附近各自行街<br />\n一個唔小心，班狗就會咬到遊客<br />\n就真係外交風波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲狗走左就出翻嚟<br />\n做真真正正Be water！🤤<br />\n<br />\n輪更制！可能係全港最大既公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/letwechangeHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FletwechangeHk&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGM